1    C           *IN94     IFEQ '0'
|2   C           A3SKJY    IFEQ 'D'
||   C           A3SKHZ    ANDLE*DATE
||   C                     ITER
|2   C                     ENDIF
|2   C           *DATE     IFGE A3UKHZ
||   C           *DATE     ANDLEA3STHZ
||   C* OK
